	VirtualMailManager/serviceset.py, VirtualMailManager/transport.py,
	setup.py, update_config.py, vmm:
	Updated copyright notices to include the year 2012.
	[14abdd04ddf5] <v0.6.x>

	* TODO:
	TODO: Removed "listpwschemes" entry. Was done with changeset
	a64c1b5e08b4
	[11ed67ee7ebb] <v0.6.x>

