	[b0165b7af7a3] <v0.6.x>

	* VirtualMailManager/account.py:
	VMM/account: Check the account's transport only when we have a
	transport.
	[2662f4e17eb4] <v0.6.x>

	* VirtualMailManager/account.py,
	VirtualMailManager/cli/subcommands.py,
